# **ASSIGNMENT (TE-12)**

**Task:**

Assemble your binder (digital or PDF) using the 10-section format.

**Checklist:**

- Snapshot page completed
- Legal documents organized
- Inventory attached
- Valuation attached
- Exhibits A/B/C inserted
- Communication organized
- Distribution plan ready
- Insurance section filled
- Receipts/Releases drafted
- Emotional dynamics noted

**Upload:**

Export your Notion workspace or binder PDF and store it in the Final Archive.

